snippet.title: Atlantic '41 (game for Playdate) - Bridge view with first coastal ocean sound test and sea birds
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay record of the bridge view from my upcoming U-boat simulator "Atlantic '41", running on the Playdate portable console.
First tests of implementing ambient coastal ocean sounds and sea birds.
